"image)"
msgstr "ລາຍຊື່ສິນຄ້າທີ່ເລືອກເຊິ່ງກົງກັບເງື່ອນໄຂ (ມີບາໂຄດ ແລະ ບໍ່ມີຮູບພາບ)"

#. module: product_barcodelookup
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/product_barcodelookup/wizard/product_fetch_image_wizard.py:0
msgid ""
"The scheduled action \"Product Images: Get product images from Barcode "
"Lookup\" has been deleted. Please contact your administrator to have the "
"action restored or to reinstall the module \"product_barcodelookup\"."
msgstr ""
"ການເຮັດວຽກຕາມກຳນົດເວລາ \"Product Images: Get product images from Barcode "
"Lookup\" ຖືກລົບອອກແລ້ວ. ກະລຸນາຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບເພື່ອຄືນຄ່າ ຫຼື ຕິດຕັ້ງໂມດູນ "
"\"product_barcodelookup\" ໃໝ່."

